ikh, ikh

00:25:16.826 --> 00:25:19.560
ge- gedenk, me hot geleyent Sholem Aleykhemen

00:25:19.560 --> 00:25:22.029
ikh b- ikh b- dos gedenk ikh nit.

00:25:22.812 --> 00:25:24.611
vos vil ikh nokh zogn?

