az in geto, ikh hob dertseylt az ikh hob geshtrikt far

00:25:30.444 --> 00:25:32.896
kh'hob gearbet in MAST- UNK di varshtatn

00:25:32.953 --> 00:25:37.739
ober di lage iz geven zeyer a shvere in materyel, azoy vi ikh hob gut geshtrikt

00:25:38.117 --> 00:25:39.798
hob ikh geshtrikt

00:25:40.193 --> 00:25:45.134
afile loy- oyf bashtelungen. mentshn flegn oysht- oystrenen eyn zakh

00:25:45.134 --> 00:25:46.566
s'iz dort geven kalt.

00:25:46.690 --> 00:25:50.346
s'iz geven farsheydene

00:25:50.841 --> 00:25:52.989
ot ikh veys, ikh hob dem ershtn mol

00:25:52.989 --> 00:25:54.666
gedarft, m'hot mir gebrakht

00:25:54.840 --> 00:25:56.791
a kleyd ikh zol shtrikn.

00:25:57.777 --> 00:26:01.703
nit kh'hob gevust vi men shtrikt. e- bluzkes hob ikh geshtrikt.

00:26:02.097 --> 00:26:04.751
kh'hob gezogt az ikh veys vi tsu shtrikn.

00:26:04.751 --> 00:26:07.203
v- ⟨vi⟩ ikh vel zikh nit opzogn fun dem.

00:26:07.463 --> 00:26:08.649
dos iz geven

00:26:09.319 --> 00:26:13.413
daytshishe hentshkes, grine, geforbn oyf shvarts

00:26:13.791 --> 00:26:16.097
un nokh kolirt UNK ⟨hot men⟩ gebrakht

00:26:16.120 --> 00:26:19.624
ober vi, vi veyst men vi tsu shtrikn a kleyd?

00:26:19.765 --> 00:26:22.706
bay LYALE MARGOLES iz geven a kleyd

00:26:22.706 --> 00:26:25.041
velkhe di muter hot ir oysgeshtrikt.

00:26:25.367 --> 00:26:27.436
ikh bin avek tsu ir in shtub

00:26:27.780 --> 00:26:29.816
un ikh hob ibergetseylt

00:26:30.058 --> 00:26:32.110
ale ⟨pekes⟩ fun der kleyd

00:26:32.303 --> 00:26:37.413
un loyt dem vi ikh hob farshribn, hob ikh dervust az ⟨loyt⟩ der driter rey darf ikh dergebn azoy fil

00:26:37.413 --> 00:26:40.693
loyt der ah zekster rey azoy fil, un azoy vayter.

00:26:40.693 --> 00:26:44.470
dos iz geven mayn ershte z- kleyd vos ikh hob geshtrikt in geto

00:26:44.487 --> 00:26:45.462
vayle

00:26:45.462 --> 00:26:46.792
lebn hot men

00:26:46.849 --> 00:26:47.889
gedarft

00:26:47.889 --> 00:26:50.759
un fun dest vegn az me flegt oysshtrikn, flegt men epes

00:26:50.759 --> 00:26:54.639
UNK geshtrikt hob ikh ge- kimat di nekht UNK vayle bay tog hob ikh gedarft arbetn

00:26:54.747 --> 00:26:56.735
dos ikh oykh geven aza min zakh.

00:26:56.735 --> 00:27:00.765
nu, s'iz geven. nor eyn zakh iz mir geven zeyer veytikdik.

00:27:02.998 --> 00:27:05.320
ikh hob gehat zeyer sheyne voln

00:27:05.320 --> 00:27:06.885
far zikh sh-

