mayne a mume hot gearbet in a krom

00:27:12.229 --> 00:27:14.284
vu es, me hot, flegt farkoyfn

00:27:14.284 --> 00:27:15.432
vol

00:27:16.478 --> 00:27:20.849
oystsuneyen farsheydene zakhn ongehoybene

00:27:20.849 --> 00:27:22.922
un ikh hob gehat zeyer sheyne

00:27:24.531 --> 00:27:26.299
zayd azoyne

00:27:26.299 --> 00:27:29.949
kedey tsu sh- a- in roz, lil

